{"tid":2487226,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佩雷斯自動連任皇馬會長","createTime":"2021-04-13T11:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:48:43.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a20b27d4fc46b540dd4e9f6960886ca807da1f7","tid":2487226,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】西甲豪門皇家馬德里官方宣佈，會長佩雷斯在沒有競爭對手之下，成功連任。<br />\n年屆74歲的商人佩雷斯（Florentino P&eacute;rez）自動連任皇家馬德里會長，亦是第6次當選，新任期將於2025年屆滿。<br />\n<br />\n佩雷斯早在2000年擊敗前會長辛斯，首次當選，同時皇馬巨額引入多名巨星包括費高、施丹、朗拿度等，為人津津樂道。2004年成功連任後，球隊成績走下坡，這名商人決定在2006年2月請辭。<br />\n<br />\n2009年，佩雷斯捲土重來，再次當選皇馬會長，今次簽下了卡卡、基斯坦奴朗拿度等當時得令的球星，及後一直連任至今，最威水的成績當然是取得歐聯3連冠，上季亦重奪西甲錦標。<br />\n<br />\n皇馬原本在今夏舉行大選，但門檻甚高，競選人必須成為會員20年或以上，同時擁有西班牙國籍，更要遞交球會15%的年度預算作為保證金，以今次大選為例，保證金達到1.2億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"eea330912af20ab30ca108b4522515ff575c3c52","tid":2487226,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾 冇人情味"},{"pid":"1f28c68582a398cd8701549bf240d1045ee05901","tid":2487226,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76621500487bfb3d05166bf19c9d4fe0982d10c","tid":2487226,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EyzgWPtWYAchOEe?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEyzgWPtWYAchOEe%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=098d8158&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdad32d14d2de0161a7e291f5204effc3ae4da13","tid":2487226,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"肉酸又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}